title: Woman Feeding Baby Medium Skin Tone

description: A woman with a medium skin tone is shown breastfeeding or bottle-feeding her baby. This emoji represents nurturing, motherhood, and the act of feeding an infant.

The gentle curves of both figures, enhanced by Apple's soft rounded edges and realistic lighting, create a warm and intimate scene. The mother's expression, rendered with subtle gradients and a loving gaze, is particularly touching, making this emoji on Apple devices a perfect symbol of parental love, nourishment, and familial bonds.
